  "keyFeatures": [
    "Create and manage multiple custom maps with configurable visibility (private, public, unlisted)",
    "Add custom markers anywhere on the map with icons, colors, notes, and place data",
    "Organize markers into collections with custom icons and colors",
    "Draw paths and shapes (lines, circles, rectangles, polygons) with real-time measurements",
    "Add visual labels with custom icons and colors to map regions",
    "Real-time collaborative editing with role-based permissions (owner, editor, viewer, commenter)",
    "Share maps via links or invite specific users with granular permission levels",
    "Duplicate entire maps including all markers, collections, paths, and routes",
    "Multiple map styles: hybrid, roadmap, satellite, terrain",
    "Integrated place data from Google Maps, Mapbox, and Foursquare",
    "Route planning with multi-stop support and travel type selection (driving, walking, transit, bicycling)"
  ],
